	<div class="unit whole help-instructions">
		<h3>
			How do I upload an attachment?
		</h3>
		<hr>
		<p>
			To upload an attachment, click on a current assignment (either "In-Progress" or "Assigned") you wish to add the attachment too.
		</p>
		<p>
			Once viewing the assignment details, tap the navigation icon in the top right of your screen and select "Add Attachment".
			You can also get to the navigation by swiping your finger from right to left on the screen.
		</p>
		<p>
			Next click on "choose file" and you will be prompted to either "Choose Existing" or "Take Photo or Video".
		</p>
		<p>
			Once you have selected the correct attachment click "Upload".
		</p>
